OL,7,FActor and former GB News presenter
OL,8,FLaurence Fox has been charged with a
OL,9,Fsexual offence after allegedly sharing
OL,10,Fa compromising photo of TV star
OL,11,FNarinder Kaur on social media.
OL,13,FIn a tweet posted in April 2024, the
OL,14,F46-year-old is said to have shared a
OL,15,Fcompromising image of the broadcaster
OL,16,Fwho appears regularly on Good Morning
OL,17,FBritain and has previously appeared on
OL,18,FGB News.
