OL,7,FPosting on X at the time, Kaur, 52,
OL,8,Fsaid the image was "unimaginably
OL,9,Fmortifying".
OL,11,FFox addressed the situation in an
OL,12,Fextended post the following day, in
OL,13,Fwhich he said he "would like to
OL,14,Fapologise" to Kaur and then went on to
OL,15,Fsay, "it's not my fault" Kaur was
OL,16,Fpictured in the compromising image
OL,17,Fmore than 15 years ago.
OL,19,FPolice have charged Fox after an 11-
OL,20,Fmonth investigation. He is due to
OL,21,Fappear in court in April.
