OL,7,FA Metropolitan Police spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "A man has been charged with a
OL,9,Fsexual offence following an
OL,10,Finvestigation by the Metropolitan
OL,11,FPolice.
OL,13,F"Laurence Fox, 46, will appear at
OL,14,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,15,FApril 24 charged with an offence
OL,16,Fcontrary to section 66A of the Sexual
OL,17,FOffences Act 2003.
OL,19,F"The charge relates to an image that
OL,20,Fwas posted on a social media platform
OL,21,Fin April 2024."
