OL,7,FSection 66A of the Sexual Offences Act
OL,8,Frelates to "cyber flashing".
OL,10,FThe charge was introduced in 2023 and
OL,11,Fmakes it an offence to intentionally
OL,12,Fshare a sexual image of someone
OL,13,Fwithout consent, with the aim of
OL,14,Fcausing alarm, distress, humiliation,
OL,15,For for sexual gratification.
