OL,7,FUpskirting, taking pictures of people
OL,8,Funder their clothes without their
OL,9,Fpermission, became a specific criminal
OL,10,Foffence in 2019. Offenders can face up
OL,11,Fto two years in jail and be placed on
OL,12,Fthe sex offenders register.
OL,14,FFox, of Peldon, Essex, was fired from
OL,15,FGB News in October 2023 after an on-
OL,16,Fair rant about journalist Ava Evans.
